  <heading type="short">Fiscal Year 2017 Revised Local BudgetTemporary Adjustment Act of 2017</heading>
  <heading type="long">To adjust, on anTemporary basis, certain allocations in the Fiscal Year 2017 Local Budget Act of 2016 pursuant to the Omnibus Appropriations Act, 2009.</heading>
