    </codify:annotation>
  </section>
  <section>
    <num>3</num>
    <heading>Remaining Fiscal Year 2017 unexpended revenue of $194,011,000 shall be carried over into Fiscal Year 2018 as fund balance and shall be available as set forth in the approved Fiscal Year 2018 Budget and Financial Plan.</heading>
  </section>
  <section>
    <num>4</num>
    <heading>Fifty percent of all Fiscal Year 2017 local agency underspending certified in the Fiscal Year 2017 Comprehensive Annual Financial Report shall be allocated to the Workforce Investments account to pay for salary increases or other items required by the terms of collective bargaining agreements that will become effective in Fiscal Year 2018 and beyond.</heading>
  </section>
